      "rendered": "Global NGO Technology Report"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>Released on September 16, 2019, the <a href=\"https://funraise.org/techreport\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 Global NGO Technology Report</strong></a> examines how NGOs worldwide use web and email communications, online fundraising tools, social media, mobile technology, and productivity software.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://funraise.org/techreport\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-24306 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2019-Global-NGO-Technology-Report-Blue-Small.png?resize=600%2C300\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2019-Global-NGO-Technology-Report-Blue-Small.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/2019-Global-NGO-Technology-Report-Blue-Small.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3><strong>In Spanish, Portuguese, and French</strong></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2019-Tech-Report-Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 Informe Global sobre Tecnolog\u00eda de ONG</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2019-Tech-Report-Portuguese.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 Relat\u00f3rio Global de Tecnologia ONG</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2019-Tech-Report-French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2019 rapport sur l\u2019utilisation des technologies par les organisations nongouvernementales (ONG) mondiales</strong></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Previous Editions</strong></h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2018-Tech-Report-English.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Global NGO Technology Report</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-Tech-Report-Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Informe Global sobre Tecnolog\u00eda de ONG</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-Tech-Report-Portuguese.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 Relat\u00f3rio Global de Tecnologia ONG</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2018-Tech-Report-French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2018 rapport sur l\u2019utilisation des technologies par les organisations nongouvernementales (ONG) mondiales</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-Tech-Report-English-FINAL.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Global NGO Technology Report</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-NGO-Tech-Report_Spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 Informe Global sobre Tecnolog\u00eda de ONG</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2017-NGO-Tech-Report_French.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2017 rapport sur l\u2019utilisation des technologies par les organisations nongouvernementales (ONG) mondiales</a></strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2016-Global-NGO-Online-Technology-Report-FINAL.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>2016 Global NGO Technology Report</strong></a></p>\n<h3>Related Research</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/global-trends-in-giving-report/\"><strong>The Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\"><strong>The Open Data Project</strong></a></p>\n",
